@startuml
title Registration Use Case Activity Diagram

start

:Customer navigates to Registration page;
:Enter required details (email, password, name, etc.);
:Submit registration form to backend;

:Backend validates data;
if (Data valid?) then (yes)
  :Create new user account;
  :Generate JWT for session;
  :Store JWT in AuthContext;
  :Redirect to Product Page;
else (no)
  :Show error message;
  :Allow retry or correct data;
endif

stop
@enduml
